k_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#verifyGrind\"><span class=\"name\">verifyGrind</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config\">Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Verify that `grind?` suggestions actually work. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#verifyGrind","kind":"def","line":673,"name":"verifyGrind","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L673-L677"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.verifyGrind\"><span class=\"name\">linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">tacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">verifyGrind</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Verify that `grind?` suggestions actually work. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.verifyGrind","kind":"opaque","line":668,"name":"linter.tacticAnalysis.verifyGrind","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L668-L671"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.verifyTryThisSuggestions\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">TacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">verifyTryThisSuggestions</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">tac</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Lean.Syntax</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">Lean.MVarId</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Command.html#Lean.Elab.Command.CommandElabM\">Lean.Elab.Command.CommandElabM</a> (<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TSyntax\">Lean.TSyntax</a> <span class=\"fn\">`tactic</span>)</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">label</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config\">Config</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Verify that TryThis suggestions from a tactic actually work.\n\nRuns the given tactic at each proof step, captures any \"Try this:\" suggestions,\nthen re-runs the suggested tactic to verify it succeeds.\nOnly reports failures (where the suggestion doesn't close the goal). ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.verifyTryThisSuggestions","kind":"def","line":586,"name":"Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.verifyTryThisSuggestions","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L586-L666"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.introMerge\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">TacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">introMerge</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config\">Config</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Suggest merging two adjacent `intro` tactics which don't pattern match. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.introMerge","kind":"def","line":552,"name":"Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.introMerge","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L552-L571"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.introMerge\"><span class=\"name\">linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">tacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">introMerge</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Suggest merging two adjacent `intro` tactics which don't pattern match. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.introMerge","kind":"opaque","line":547,"name":"linter.tacticAnalysis.introMerge","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L547-L550"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#tryAtEachStepFromEnv\"><span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStepFromEnv</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config\">Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run a custom tactic at every step in proofs, configured via environment variables.\n\nSet `TRY_AT_EACH_STEP_TACTIC` to the tactic syntax to try (required).\nSet `TRY_AT_EACH_STEP_LABEL` to the label for output messages (optional, defaults to tactic).\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#tryAtEachStepFromEnv","kind":"def","line":542,"name":"tryAtEachStepFromEnv","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L542-L544"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepFromEnv\"><span class=\"name\">linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">tacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStepFromEnv</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run a custom tactic at every step in proofs, configured via environment variables.\n\nSet `TRY_AT_EACH_STEP_TACTIC` to the tactic syntax to try (required).\nSet `TRY_AT_EACH_STEP_LABEL` to the label for output messages (optional, defaults to tactic).\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepFromEnv","kind":"opaque","line":533,"name":"linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepFromEnv","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L533-L540"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#tryAtEachStepSimpAllSuggestions\"><span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStepSimpAllSuggestions</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config\">Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run `simp_all? +suggestions` at every step in proofs, reporting where it succeeds. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#tryAtEachStepSimpAllSuggestions","kind":"def","line":529,"name":"tryAtEachStepSimpAllSuggestions","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L529-L531"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepSimpAllSuggestions\"><span class=\"name\">linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">tacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStepSimpAllSuggestions</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run `simp_all? +suggestions` at every step in proofs, reporting where it succeeds. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepSimpAllSuggestions","kind":"opaque","line":524,"name":"linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepSimpAllSuggestions","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L524-L527"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#tryAtEachStepGrindSuggestions\"><span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStepGrindSuggestions</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis.html#Mathli