></div>","info":{"doc":"Run `aesop` at every step in proofs, reporting where it succeeds. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#tryAtEachStepAesop","kind":"def","line":508,"name":"tryAtEachStepAesop","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L508-L513"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepAesop\"><span class=\"name\">linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">tacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStepAesop</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run `aesop` at every step in proofs, reporting where it succeeds. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepAesop","kind":"opaque","line":503,"name":"linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepAesop","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L503-L506"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#tryAtEachStepSimpAll\"><span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStepSimpAll</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config\">Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run `simp_all` at every step in proofs, reporting where it succeeds. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#tryAtEachStepSimpAll","kind":"def","line":499,"name":"tryAtEachStepSimpAll","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L499-L501"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepSimpAll\"><span class=\"name\">linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">tacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStepSimpAll</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run `simp_all` at every step in proofs, reporting where it succeeds. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepSimpAll","kind":"opaque","line":494,"name":"linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepSimpAll","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L494-L497"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#tryAtEachStepGrind\"><span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStepGrind</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config\">Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run `grind` at every step in proofs, reporting where it succeeds. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#tryAtEachStepGrind","kind":"def","line":490,"name":"tryAtEachStepGrind","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L490-L492"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepGrind\"><span class=\"name\">linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">tacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStepGrind</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run `grind` at every step in proofs, reporting where it succeeds. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepGrind","kind":"opaque","line":485,"name":"linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepGrind","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L485-L488"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepFromEnvImpl\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">TacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStepFromEnvImpl</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config\">Config</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run a custom tactic at each proof step, configured via environment variables.\n\nReads from environment variables:\n- `TRY_AT_EACH_STEP_TACTIC`: Tactic syntax to try (e.g., \"grind +suggestions\") - required\n- `TRY_AT_EACH_STEP_LABEL`: Human-readable label for output (optional, defaults to tactic)\n\nIf `TRY_AT_EACH_STEP_TACTIC` is missing, this linter does nothing.\n\nTo enable, add to the `mathlibOnlyLinters` array in `lakefile.lean`:\n```lean\n⟨`linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepFromEnv, true⟩,\n```\n\nThen run with the environment variable:\n```bash\nTRY_AT_EACH_STEP_TACTIC=\"grind +suggestions\" lake build Mathlib\n```\n\nThis generic entry point is used by the hammer-bench benchmarking tool\n(https://github.com/leanprover-community/hammer-bench) to test arbitrary tactics\nwithout requiring Mathlib code changes for each new tactic variant.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepFromEnvImpl","kind":"def","line":457,"name":"Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepFromEnvImpl","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L457-L483"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepFromStrings\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">TacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStepFromStrings</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">label </span><span class=\"fn\">tacticStr</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config\">Config</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run a tactic (given as a string) at each proof step, with optional timing.\n\n`label` is the human-readable name shown in output (e.g., \"grind\").\n`tacticStr` is the tactic syntax as a string (e.g., \"grind +suggestions\").\nTactic sequences like \"simp; grind\" are also supported.\n\nReports elapsed time in milliseconds for each successful replacement\nwhen `linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep.showTiming` is true.\nTo limit tactic runtime, use `set_option maxHeartbeats N` in the build command.\n\nWhen `linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep.selfReplacements` is false, cases where\nthe suggested tactic matches the existing proof are suppressed.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepFromStrings","kind":"def","line":430,"name":"Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepFromStrings","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L430-L455"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">TacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">tac</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Lean.Syntax</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">Lean.MVarId</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Command.html#Lean.Elab.Command.CommandElabM\">Lean.Elab.Command.CommandElabM</a> (<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TSyntax\">Lean.TSyntax</a> <span class=\"fn\">`tactic</span>)</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config\">Config</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run a tactic at each proof step. See `tryAtEachStepCore` for details. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep","kind":"def","line":425,"name":"Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L425-L428"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepCore\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">TacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStepCore</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">tac</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Lean.Syntax</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">Lean.MVarId</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Command.html#Lean.Elab.Command.CommandElabM\">Lean.Elab.Command.CommandElabM</a> (<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TSyntax\">Lean.TSyntax</a> <span class=\"fn\">`tactic</span>)</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">label</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option.none\">none</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.Config\">Config</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Run a tactic at each proof step, with optional timing.\n\n`label` is an optional human-readable name for output. If `none`, the tactic syntax is used.\n\nReports elapsed time in milliseconds for each successful replacement\nwhen `linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep.showTiming` is true.\n\nWhen `linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep.selfReplacements` is false, cases where\nthe suggested tactic matches the existing proof are suppressed.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepCore","kind":"def","line":370,"name":"Mathlib.TacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStepCore","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L370-L423"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep.selfReplacements\"><span class=\"name\">linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">tacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStep</span>.<span class=\"name\">selfReplacements</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Whether to report when a tactic can be replaced with itself.\n\nWhen true (default), all successful replacements are reported, including when\nthe suggested tactic matches the existing proof.\nWhen false, self-replacements are suppressed.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep.selfReplacements","kind":"opaque","line":359,"name":"linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep.selfReplacements","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L359-L368"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep.showTiming\"><span class=\"name\">linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">tacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStep</span>.<span class=\"name\">showTiming</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Whether to show timing information in \"tryAtEachStep\" tactic analysis output.\n\nWhen true (default), messages include elapsed time like `(23ms)`.\nSet to false in tests to avoid non-deterministic output.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep.showTiming","kind":"opaque","line":349,"name":"linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep.showTiming","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L349-L357"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep.fraction\"><span class=\"name\">linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">tacticAnalysis</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryAtEachStep</span>.<span class=\"name\">fraction</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"When running the \"tryAtEachStep\" tactic analysis linters,\nonly run on a fraction `1/n` of the goals found in the library.\n\nThis is useful for running quick benchmarks.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep.fraction","kind":"opaque","line":339,"name":"linter.tacticAnalysis.tryAtEachStep.fraction","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.lean#L339-L347"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/TacticAnalysis/Declarations.html#Mathl